<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Application status mail</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>
      We hope this message finds you well. We wanted to inform you about the
      status of your tutor application with
      <strong><%= process.env.APP_NAME %></strong>.
    </p>

    <% if (status === 'accepted') { %>
    <p>
      Congratulations! We are pleased to inform you that your application has
      been approved. We were impressed with your qualifications and believe you
      will be a valuable addition to our team of tutors.
    </p>
    <p>
      Next Steps: Please log in to your account on our platform to complete any
      remaining setup steps and start connecting with students.
    </p>
    <% } else if (status === 'rejected') { %>
    <p>
      We regret to inform you that after careful consideration, we have decided
      not to move forward with your application at this time. This decision was
      not easy, as we received many strong applications.
    </p>
    <p>
      Feedback: If you would like feedback on your application or suggestions
      for future applications, please feel free to reach out to us.
    </p>
    <% } %>

    <p>
      We appreciate the time and effort you invested in your application and
      encourage you to apply again in the future.
    </p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><strong>The <%= process.env.APP_NAME %> Team</strong></p>

  </body>
</html>
